g me and my agent talked about when we went in and I signed with the team,\\\" Owens said,\\u00c2viaThe Associated Press.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999998350163105, \"rank\": 1.649807308913188e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"my agent\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"Owens\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was all respectful.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We went to them and just asked, 'We would really appreciate it if he could go and support his wife,' and they were really cool about it.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First-class organization.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"First-class organization\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to thank them so much for allowing me to go over and do that.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait to be able to support her, and I know my family and my wife, she really appreciates it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles's Olympic run begins on Sunday, July 28 with the qualifying round.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrase